{"tid":1525902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟同我做機場交通壓力測試","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:31:16.000Z","uid":62778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a89510ce5842e96b8f39ae75f819dd631166f09d","tid":1525902,"uid":62778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:30:36.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8bx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=0f24ca6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9729dde2f3aea02d71b13cf5b7092fa2f606b72","tid":1525902,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:32:57.000Z","msg":"起身入機場遊車河喇"},{"pid":"da00c3c12a3246e3f29a3af54cb511be2e3fb4c8","tid":1525902,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2